---
name: Mind Map
description: Diagram type — Mind Map
tags: [diagram-type, conceptual, aspect-1:1]
inputs:
  subject:
    type: string
    default: topics in modern web development
---
Create a mind map radiating outward from a central concept. Main branches should represent major themes, with sub-branches for details. Use color coding to distinguish different branches. Keep text concise and use icons where helpful. The subject of this diagram is: {{subject}}.
